{"tid":2085756,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四個警察職方協會聯合聲明全力支持通過港區國安法草案","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T05:30:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6dacd8a9ff2f3840897d275ec7a9a3b3f2a24e","tid":2085756,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"四個警察職方協會發表聯合聲明，表示全力支持全國人大常委會審議和通過港區國安法草案。<br />\n<br />\n警務處警司協會、警務督察協會、海外督察協會及警察隊員佐級協會在聲明中表示，過去一年因反修例風波而起的暴力示威浪潮席捲全港，香港陷入史無前例的撕裂和動蕩，政治主張變質成本土恐怖主義，但煽惑者正利用香港國家安全方面的漏洞而未有受到法律的制裁，更有部分意見領袖多次出訪，游說外國政府對香港實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，一旦相關法律草案獲得人大常委會通過，警隊必將悉力配合，按相關法例公平公正專業執法，保障香港整體利益，堅定不移維護國家安全和發展大局。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534859-20200630.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534859-20200630.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CLzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=28633793\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534859-20200630.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7331573e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534859-20200630.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8a9e7109805b8a2f9e166dda52f981b721b2c2a6","tid":2085756,"uid":2054,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:25:26.000Z","msg":"制裁名單"},{"pid":"42711c8132ca7e31af306935b7403226db07dc7d","tid":2085756,"uid":177168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"支持美軍斬殺三萬港警"},{"pid":"35ce4230fdf9dab58d190468c318316971d2c4c6","tid":2085756,"uid":49588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"香港警察會公平執法！<br />\n<br />\n真是天大的笑話<br />\n<br />\n同「一國兩制」一樣，荒謬絕倫"},{"pid":"22aaf00b7a93f44c0b2c67e86ff43431871a8ee1","tid":2085756,"uid":49588,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:30:04.000Z","msg